    "Notable is also that these differences mainly are present before the financial crisis while there seems to be a slight convergence since the GFC.",
    "This can be explained by the fact that following the GFC, advanced economies saw themselves confronted with similar problems developing and autocratic countries had already experienced.",
    "One can see that this convergence is less strong for monetary-financial coordination, namely there is a continuously higher need to coordinate for non-democracies.",
    "This latter finding could also indicate that autocracies have to do more efforts in general to contain market pressures.",
